      >
    </ContentWrapper>

    <div
      data-fade-list
      data-prevent-flicker="true"
      class="wws_deliverables_list"
    >
      <div class="wws_deliverables_group">
        <Heading tag="h3" variant="h4" marginBottom={0}
          >Both Tiers Include</Heading
        >
        <ul class="u-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Content updates.</strong> Text changes, image swaps, product updates,
            pricing changes. You send it, we handle it.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>CMS management.</strong> Blog posts you've written get formatted
            and published. Team pages, portfolios, product catalogs, FAQ entries.
            Anything that lives in your CMS, we keep it current.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Performance maintenance.</strong> Speed improvements, mobile responsiveness,
            broken link fixes. The site stays healthy between updates.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Webflow hosting and platform support.</strong> We monitor your
            Webflow project for issues and handle platform-level concerns so you don't
            have to think about them.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="wws_deliverables_group">
        <Heading maxWidth="40ch" tag="h3" variant="h4" marginBottom={0}
          >Growth Support Also Includes</Heading
        >
        <ul class="u-list">
          <li>
            <strong>New landing pages.</strong> Campaign pages, service pages, event
            pages. You tell us what the page needs to do. We design and build it.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Section and component design.</strong> New headers, CTA blocks,
            feature sections, testimonial layouts, pricing tables. If your site needs
            a new section, we build it.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Form builds and CRM connections.</strong> Contact forms, intake
            forms, application forms connected to your CRM, email platform, or automation
            tool. We make sure submissions go where they need to go.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Lead magnet design and deployment.</strong> You write the guide,
            checklist, or framework. We design it, build the landing page, connect
            the form, and set up the delivery. (If you need someone to write it too,
            that's a <a
              href="/services/marketing-partner"
              class="u-text-style-underline">Marketing Partner</a
            > conversation.)
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Custom interactions and integrations.</strong> Animations, scroll-based
            effects, third-party tool integrations, embed configurations. The development
            work that makes your site feel polished and functional.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="wws_deliverables_group">
        <Heading tag="h3" variant="h4" marginBottom={0}
          >What's Not Included</Heading
        >
        <Text marginBottom={0}
          >Website Support is execution-focused. We build what you bring us.</Text
        >
        <ul class="u-list">
          <li>
            <strong
              >Strategy, content planning, and consulting are not part of this
              service.</strong
